    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:48:48.21+09:00">孟子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:49:51.38+09:00">你不該當做你自己的心所說不該當做的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:50:33.222+09:00">你不該當欲你自己的心所說不該當欲的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-20a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:54:52.022+09:00">這樣就罷了。　　這是按雷格氏並古危勒兒的注解繙sic!譯的.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T18:41:38.684+09:00">告子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T18:48:41.198+09:00">生是那所謂的性。　[告子的意思是，性不是別的，只是生，而且生活之力一切所發現的效驗，都是性，不問善惡，並萬物之裡頭，只有一個生活之理，所以萬物也只有一個性，部分別善惡。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:05:41.516+09:00">孟子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:06:38.965+09:00">生是那所謂的性，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:10:11.662+09:00">你說這個如同說凡白顏色的都是稱為白麼？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:10:35.126+09:00">告子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-8a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:10:41.064+09:00">是的。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:11:46.541+09:00">孟子說：白羽之白</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-8a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:11:47.129+09:00">是如同白雪的白麼？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-8a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:12:05.249+09:00">白雪的白</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-9a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:12:19.962+09:00">是如同白玉之白麼？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-9a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:12:28.357+09:00">告子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:21:53.204+09:00">是的。 [孟子的意思失在那個白有分別。白羽，白雪，白玉他們的顏色都有一點不一樣，乃告子不允許。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:13:30.011+09:00">孟子說：按照這樣全的性</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:14:18.865+09:00">就是如牛之性，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:15:19.291+09:00">牛的性</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T20:08:22.334+09:00">就是如人的性?</seg>
                </p>
